{"id":"create","evals":["c0","p4"],"desc":"start a solving session","method":"POST","path":"/sessions","body":{"problem":{"title":"Bicycle frame","statement":"frame must be lighter but thinner walls lose strength under load"}},"capture":{"sid":"session_id"},"expect":{"status":201,"json_has":["session_id"]}}
{"id":"analyze","evals":["c0","p4"],"desc":"agent suggests improving/preserving parameters","method":"POST","path":"/sessions/{sid}/analyze","body":{},"expect":{"status":200,"json_has":["analysis.improving.id","analysis.improving.confidence","analysis.preserving.id"]}}
{"id":"set-params","evals":["p4"],"desc":"expert overrides parameters (14 vs 1)","method":"PUT","path":"/sessions/{sid}/parameters","body":{"improving":14,"preserving":1},"expect":{"status":200,"equals":{"parameters.improving.id":14,"parameters.preserving.id":1}}}
{"id":"matrix","evals":["c0","p4"],"desc":"matrix cell 14x1 → real principles","method":"POST","path":"/sessions/{sid}/matrix","body":{},"expect":{"status":200,"json_has":["matrix.principles.0.id","matrix.cell.improving_id"]}}
{"id":"recommendation","evals":["c0","p4"],"desc":"synthesize recommendation from selected principles","method":"POST","path":"/sessions/{sid}/recommendation","body":{"selected_principle_ids":[1,40]},"expect":{"status":200,"json_has":["recommendation.text","metadata.version"],"equals":{"metadata.principles_applied":2}}}
{"id":"get-session","evals":["c0","p4"],"desc":"full state: decision trace + metadata + steps","method":"GET","path":"/sessions/{sid}","expect":{"status":200,"json_has":["decision_trace.0","metadata.principles_found","steps.0.duration_ms"]}}
{"id":"principle-detail","evals":["p4"],"desc":"reference: full principle text","method":"GET","path":"/principles/40","expect":{"status":200,"json_has":["name","rules.0"]}}
{"id":"session-404","evals":["c0"],"desc":"unknown session → 404","method":"GET","path":"/sessions/deadbeefdead","expect":{"status":404}}
{"id":"no-statement","evals":["c0"],"desc":"missing statement → 400","method":"POST","path":"/sessions","body":{"problem":{}},"expect":{"status":400}}
